high_descs: walk forwards to the picture on the wall to the right, turn left and walk over to the coffee table
grab the remote controller closest to you off of the coffee table
move over to the end of the couch on the right side of the room
place the remote controller inside of the box on the couch
pick the box up off of the couch
turn right and walk to the wall at the end of the room, then turn to face the black chair to your left
place the box down on the black chair
anns.task_desc: place a black box with a remote controller in it on the black chair in the corner of the room

high_descs: Turn left and move to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control from the table, that is nearest the computer.
Turn to the right, then move to the end of the couch that is to the left of the door.
Place the remote into the box on the couch.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn to the right go past the door and to the chair that is to the right of the door.
Place the box on to the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a remote control into a box, move the box to a certain chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the coffee table.
Pick up the remote to the right of the laptop on the table.
Turn right towards the couch and then turn left towards the end of the couch with the box on it.
Place the remote inside the box on the couch.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn right and walk towards the chair on your left.
Place the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a tv remote on the grey chair.
